description: The Invesco BulletShares 2030 High Yield Corporate Bond ETF (Fund) is based on the BulletShares USD High Yield Corporate Bond 2030 Index (Index). The Fund will invest at least 80% of its total assets in corporate bonds that comprise the index. The Index seeks to measure the performance of a portfolio of US dollar-denominated, high yield corporate bonds with effective maturities in 2030. The Fund does not purchase all of the securities in the Index; instead, the Fund utilizes a "sampling" methodology to seek to achieve its investment objective. The Fund and the Index are rebalanced monthly. The Fund has a designated year of maturity of 2030 and will terminate on or about Dec. 15, 2030. See the prospectus for more information.
name: Invesco BulletShares 2030 High Yield Corporate Bond ETF
